enc_save_timin...traints_always(25.10)  enc_save_timin...traints_always(25.10)

Name
       enc_save_timing_constraints_always

Syntax
       enc_save_timing_constraints_always {true | false}

       Type: Boolean

       Default: false

       If true, saveDesign will copy SDC timing constraint files to the output
       directory  rather  than  keep links to the original external SDC files.
       This is the equivalent  to  always  using  the  -tcon  option  whenever
       saveDesign is called.

Related Information
              * saveDesign

